    "Additionally, the standardization and interoperability of medical data formats are vital for the widespread adoption of AI based triage systems.",
    "Ensuring that these systems can seamlessly integrate with various hospital information systems and electronic health records (EHRs) will be crucial for their effectiveness and scalability.",
    "In this study, we introduced an innovative approach for managing patient triage in emergency departments by applying artificial intelligence (AI) and network science.",
    "Utilizing machine learning algorithms and graph neural networks, our team crafted an AI module to precisely categorise patients into triage levels.",
    "In our tests, this system exhibited superior performance over conventional triage methods."
